{"tid":2036869,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透社引消息：外籍法官將被禁處理國家安全案件","createTime":"2020-05-26T17:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T00:58:03.000Z","uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d28d83f290f77ad310395aac1db0be9869a23140","tid":2036869,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:04:30.000Z","msg":"北京主動出手制定「港版國安法」激發爭議。路透社引述知情人士稱，「港版國安法」計劃禁止外籍法官處理有關國家安全的案件。報道形容，這將會進一步加劇外界對香港司法獨立的憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n報道指目前香港 23 名終審法院，有 15 人是外籍法官。在新的國安法之下，他們將不能處理涉及國安的案件，但其他民事、金融等案件則不受影響。路透社形容，任何限制外籍法官的措施，都很可能令到香港律師和法官震驚，擔憂香港司法獨立受中共領導層威脅。<br />\n<br />\n本身有提案要求人大代港訂立國安法的港區人大陳曼琪曾建議，在本港司法機關內，設立專門的國家安全法庭負責處理案件，法官都是無外國居留權及有中國籍，警務處則增設香港國家安全部負責執法。"},{"pid":"fd5cdf60dead45da1033055141e69aba3f548640","tid":2036869,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果5.27失敗 有plan B</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2036797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2036797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"acc8826b0aa8b48fe4f5ce27d7889ae30d233a85","tid":2036869,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d5852c1d7bfc754a9f8cecdf65dab3012ea4c9","tid":2036869,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:50:35.000Z","msg":"公然種族歧視"},{"pid":"9adb98aa386fe744308723ef6aa504e775bbe7d8","tid":2036869,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:53:44.000Z","msg":"中共愈難睇 滅亡愈快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af935388ad68157934000e588cba00188526108a","tid":2036869,"